Browser
   â†“
Node Container (email-app)
   â†“
MongoDB Container (mongo)



mongo is container name


Docker network provides DNS


localhost is NEVER used between containers



ğŸ”¥ INTERVIEW GOLD LINE

â€œIn Docker, containers communicate using service/container names via Docker network DNS, not localhost.â€


